thread_replies.author: Accordingtoseth
thread_replies.text: Just walked out of The Housemaid and holy shit! I was on the edge of my seat the entire time. Twist after twist until it punches you in the face. Amanda Seyfried is great, but Sydney Sweeney absolutely steals the movie. A full-on powerhouse performance. Do not skip seeing this in
